# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:10
translate portuguese mills1_de9fb575:

    # "As soon as I go into Mrs. Mills office to start working, I know something is wrong."
    "Assim que entro no escritório da Sra. Mills para começar a trabalhar, sei que algo está errado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:12
translate portuguese mills1_46eab517:

    # "Mrs. Mills stands up from her desk and walks up to me as soon as I shut the door."
    "A Sra. Mills levanta-se da secretária e aproxima-se de mim assim que fecho a porta."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:13
translate portuguese mills1_9720edc3:

    # bs "Look [pcname], you have a lot of work to do today."
    bs "Olha [pcname], tens muito trabalho para fazer hoje."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:14
translate portuguese mills1_9c04a9df:

    # bs "So I don't want you just jerking off like you have been."
    bs "Por isso, não quero que fiques aí a masturbar-te como tens feito."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:15
translate portuguese mills1_60630d5f:

    # bs "No sitting around chatting, no flirting with Dana, no staring at me when you think I'm not looking."
    bs "Não ficas aí sentado a conversar, não namoras com a Dana, não ficas a olhar para mim quando achas que não estou a ver."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:16
translate portuguese mills1_1e9feafd:

    # bs "You've been slacking off around here and I'm tired of it."
    bs "Tens andado a dar-te por vencido por aqui e estou farta disso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:17
translate portuguese mills1_bd4fb3de:

    # bs "So clean up this office. I want it cleaner than it has ever been."
    bs "Por isso, limpa este escritório. Quero-o mais limpo do que nunca."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:18
translate portuguese mills1_27d60d0e:

    # bs "I want to see you on your knees, getting all the dust out of the corners and polishing every inch of this place."
    bs "Quero ver-te de joelhos, a tirar todo o pó dos cantos e a polir cada centímetro deste lugar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:21
translate portuguese mills1_f9906f0b:

    # "I grab my supplies and immediately go to work."
    "Pego nos meus materiais e começo imediatamente a trabalhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:23
translate portuguese mills1_641fb955:

    # bs "I already told you what you did wrong. You're lazy and I'm tired of you taking advantage of my kind nature."
    bs "Já te disse o que fizeste de errado. És preguiçoso e estou farta de te ver a aproveitar-te da minha bondade."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:25
translate portuguese mills1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_nowgettowork1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_nowgettowork1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:26
translate portuguese mills1_af024200:

    # bs "Now get to work."
    bs "Agora, põe-te a trabalhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:29
translate portuguese mills1_602e4e0a:

    # bs "Oh is it?"
    bs "Ah, é?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:30
translate portuguese mills1_5e887178:

    # bs "Is it bullshit?"
    bs "É treta?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:31
translate portuguese mills1_8273c1c7:

    # bs "What I think is bullshit is my paid intern talking back to me when I told him to perform a job."
    bs "O que eu acho que é treta é o meu estagiário pago a responder-me mal quando lhe digo para fazer um trabalho."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:32
translate portuguese mills1_f88c2e68:

    # bs "Do you want me to fire you?"
    bs "Queres que te despeda?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:33
translate portuguese mills1_a4adeba2:

    # "I think about it for a moment. I don't want to be treated like this, but I also need the money and am not sure if I'd be able to get another job easily."
    "Penso nisso por um momento. Não quero ser tratado assim, mas também preciso do dinheiro e não tenho a certeza se conseguiria arranjar outro emprego facilmente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:34
translate portuguese mills1_e842297d:

    # "Especially one where I get a free car out of the deal."
    "Especialmente um em que receba um carro de graça no pacote."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:35
translate portuguese mills1_9abd97c5:

    # pc "No ma'am."
    pc "Não, senhora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:36
translate portuguese mills1_0f684137:

    # bs "Then quit your back-talk and get to work."
    bs "Então pára com as respostas insolentes e põe-te a trabalhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:38
translate portuguese mills1_196ecdb4:

    # "I get to work cleaning everything, scrubbing every surface in the place, dusting the corners like she had said."
    "Começo a limpar tudo, esfregando todas as superfícies do local, tirando o pó dos cantos, tal como ela tinha dito."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:40
translate portuguese mills1_014d684e:

    # "I'm not sure that she is actually getting any work done while I am cleaning."
    "Não tenho a certeza se ela está realmente a fazer algum trabalho enquanto eu limpo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:41
translate portuguese mills1_04589ea8:

    # "To me, it seems like she just sits there and watches me the whole time."
    "Para mim, parece que ela fica apenas sentada ali a observar-me o tempo todo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:42
translate portuguese mills1_e02d88e1:

    # bs "Be sure you get that spot over there."
    bs "Certifica-te de que limpássas bem aquela mancha ali."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:43
translate portuguese mills1_6b79327c:

    # bs "If there's a single bit of dirt left over there later, I'm going to be very upset, [pcname]."
    bs "Se mais tarde restar um único grão de sujidade ali, vou ficar muito chateada, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:44
translate portuguese mills1_27eb9444:

    # "I work like that for four hours, non-stop, until the office is closed and it is time to go home."
    "Trabalho assim durante quatro horas, sem parar, até o escritório fechar e chegar a hora de ir para casa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:46
translate portuguese mills1_e2dee895:

    # bs "Alright, stud, you can stop."
    bs "Muito bem, garanhão, podes parar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:47
translate portuguese mills1_53e9c55a:

    # bs "Stand up."
    bs "Levanta-te."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:51
translate portuguese mills1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:52
translate portuguese mills1_2ca78f08:

    # bs "You did good work today."
    bs "Fizeste um bom trabalho hoje."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:53
translate portuguese mills1_fe3292c7:

    # bs "Honestly, you do good work most days."
    bs "Sinceramente, fazes um bom trabalho na maioria dos dias."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:54
translate portuguese mills1_a79bb6dc:

    # bs "I was in a bit of a bad mood earlier and took it out on you a little."
    bs "Estava um pouco de mau humor há pouco e descarreguei um pouco em ti."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:55
translate portuguese mills1_cfb2e357:

    # bs "Sorry about that."
    bs "Desculpa por isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:56
translate portuguese mills1_be77b030:

    # bs "But seeing you on your knees working your ass off for me definitely made me feel better."
    bs "Mas ver-te de joelhos a dar o teu melhor por mim fez-me sentir definitivamente melhor."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:58
translate portuguese mills1_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:59
translate portuguese mills1_66fe2ea0:

    # bs "Thank you for that."
    bs "Obrigada por isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:60
translate portuguese mills1_aa5ddb1f:

    # bs "Anyway, go on home. Thanks for working so hard today."
    bs "De qualquer forma, vai para casa. Obrigada por teres trabalhado tanto hoje."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:61
translate portuguese mills1_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sim, senhora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:63
translate portuguese mills1_1f470382:

    # "I leave her office and head down to the lobby."
    "Saio do escritório dela e dirijo-me para o átrio."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:64
translate portuguese mills1_f1b20649:

    # "Dana had already left. I hadn't even seen her all day after work started."
    "A Dana já tinha saído. Nem sequer a vi durante todo o dia depois de o trabalho ter começado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:65
translate portuguese mills1_880f4fbb:

    # "Mrs. Mills had just wanted to see me on the floor. She seems to like that feeling of domination."
    "A Sra. Mills só queria ver-me no chão. Ela parece gostar daquela sensação de dominação."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:69
translate portuguese mills1_94c66083:

    # "I have to admit, having her dominate me like that is pretty fucking hot."
    "Tenho de admitir que ser dominado por ela dessa forma é bastante excitante."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:70
translate portuguese mills1_947d9cb0:

    # "I wonder how far she would take it."
    "Pergunto-me até onde ela iria."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:73
translate portuguese mills1_c7f17ec1:

    # "I don't like this at all. I don't want anything to do with her."
    "Não gosto nada disto. Não quero ter nada a ver com ela."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:74
translate portuguese mills1_1180df5a:

    # "This isn't going to go any further."
    "Isto não vai ir mais longe."

